query:
INSERT INTO
    duckdb_data_version (
        "version",
        matrix_month_bucket,
        duckdb_data_version_id
    )
VALUES
    ($1, $2, $3)
ON CONFLICT (duckdb_data_version_id) DO
UPDATE
SET
    "version" = duckdb_data_version.version + 1,
    matrix_month_bucket = excluded.matrix_month_bucket
